    "body": "## 📌 Description\r\n\r\nThere are a whole bunch of cases where setting the flags when building for AOT is a useful thing to do, so I added FLASHINFER_EXTRA_CFLAGS to go with the existing FLASHINFER_EXTRA_LDFLAGS\r\n\r\nAnd FLASHINFER_EXTRA_CUDAFLAGS since it seems silly to leave the job half done\r\n\r\n## 🚀 Pull Request Checklist\r\n\r\n### ✅ Pre-commit Checks\r\n\r\n- [X] I have installed `pre-commit` by running `pip install pre-commit` (or used your preferred method).\r\n- [X] I have installed the hooks with `pre-commit install`.\r\n- [X] I have run the hooks manually with `pre-commit run --all-files` and fixed any reported issues.\r\n\r\n## 🧪 Tests\r\n\r\n- [ ] Tests have been added or updated as needed.\r\n- [ ] All tests are passing (`unittest`, etc.).\r\n\r\n## Reviewer Notes\r\n",
